<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ux_client_script"><sys_ux_client_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><controller_preset/><includes/><macroponent display_value="Homepage Default">f328afddc37e9294daea9533e4013135</macroponent><name>teams_dropdown/selectedItems</name><preset/><required_translations>[]</required_translations><script><![CDATA[/**
 * @param {params} params
 * @param {api} params.api
 * @param {TransformApiHelpers} params.helpers
 */
function evaluateProperty({
    api,
    helpers
}) {
    var gt = [];
    if (api.state.dashboardId == '')
        gt.push('scrum');
    else
